    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p><strong>测试部署网站需要的各种插件，以供参照</strong></p><h2 id="代码高亮"><a href="#代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="代码高亮"></a>代码高亮</h2><ul><li>和Markdown语法相同</li></ul><blockquote><p><code>highlight</code></p></blockquote><h2 id="数学公式"><a href="#数学公式" class="headerlink" title="数学公式"></a>数学公式</h2><ul><li>和Latex语法相同</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\rho(\frac{\partial \mathbf{v}}{\partial t}+(\mathbf{v}\cdot\nabla)\mathbf{v})=-\nabla p+\mu \nabla^2\mathbf{v}+f</script><figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs taggerscript">$$<br><span class="hljs-symbol">\r</span>ho(<span class="hljs-symbol">\f</span>rac&#123;<span class="hljs-symbol">\p</span>artial <span class="hljs-symbol">\m</span>athbf&#123;v&#125;&#125;&#123;<span class="hljs-symbol">\p</span>artial t&#125;+(<span class="hljs-symbol">\m</span>athbf&#123;v&#125;<span class="hljs-symbol">\c</span>dot<span class="hljs-symbol">\n</span>abla)<span class="hljs-symbol">\m</span>athbf&#123;v&#125;)=-<span class="hljs-symbol">\n</span>abla p+<span class="hljs-symbol">\m</span>u <span class="hljs-symbol">\n</span>abla^2<span class="hljs-symbol">\m</span>athbf&#123;v&#125;+f<br>$$<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="插入音频"><a href="#插入音频" class="headerlink" title="插入音频"></a>插入音频</h2><ul><li>网易云外链：(通过网页版生成)</li></ul><blockquote><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=22716498&auto=1&height=66"></iframe></blockquote><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;iframe <span class="hljs-attribute">frameborder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">marginwidth</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">marginheight</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>=330 <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>=86 <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=22716498&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>meting生成歌单：(注意markdown编辑千万别加代码高亮的```)</li></ul><blockquote>    <div id="aplayer-dOGQBkQP" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="7862539210" data-server="tencent" data-type="playlist" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86"></div></blockquote><figure class="highlight clojure"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs clojure">&#123;% meting <span class="hljs-string">&quot;7862539210&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;tencent&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;playlist&quot;</span> %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>meting生成歌单和歌曲：</li></ul><blockquote>    <div id="aplayer-dEameXCc" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker" data-id="004351Vk3uwOhB" data-server="tencent" data-type="song" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="true" data-listmaxheight="340px" data-preload="auto" data-theme="#ad7a86"></div></blockquote><figure class="highlight clojure"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs clojure">&#123;% meting <span class="hljs-string">&quot;004351Vk3uwOhB&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;tencent&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;song&quot;</span> %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>ps. qq音乐的id如加粗位置y.qq.com/n/yqq/song/<strong>004351Vk3uwOhB</strong>.html</p></blockquote><ul><li>本地音频：(aplayer实现，和meting无法同时加载)</li></ul><figure class="highlight gcode"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gcode">&#123;<span class="hljs-meta">%</span> aplayer <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Jet Hero&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;王晨淮&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Jet Hero.mp3&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-meta">%</span>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="插入图片"><a href="#插入图片" class="headerlink" title="插入图片"></a>插入图片</h2><ul><li>本地图片：（用相对路径，放在po文同名文件夹里就可以）</li></ul><blockquote><p><img src="/2021/02/05/test/a384e65513662ecb7b2178005e2e4055.jpg" alt="a384e65513662ecb7b2178005e2e4055"></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">!<span class="hljs-selector-attr">[sample]</span>(<span class="hljs-selector-tag">a384e65513662ecb7b2178005e2e4055</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.jpg</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>外链图片：(markdown语法即可)</li></ul><blockquote><p><img src="https://image.gcores.com/53c055e8-414d-45df-8998-d9f4cf4c4448.jpg?x-oss-process=image/quality,q_90/watermark,image_d2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw,g_se,x_10,y_10" alt="1"></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">![sample](https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//im</span>age.gcores.com<span class="hljs-regexp">/53c055e8-414d-45df-8998-d9f4cf4c4448.jpg?x-oss-process=image/</span>quality,q_90/watermark,image_d2F0ZXJtYXJrLnBuZw,g_se,x_10,y_10)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>图床图片：（使用<a href="https://sm.ms/">sm.ms</a>)</li></ul><blockquote><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/02/05/OiyAj73IlBeozK6.jpg" alt="4acf7ad5-19ad-4310-bbf5-79829bd4c5a9.jpg"></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">![<span class="hljs-number">4</span>acf7ad5-<span class="hljs-number">19</span>ad-<span class="hljs-number">4310</span>-bbf5-<span class="hljs-number">79829</span>bd4c5a9.jpg](https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//i</span>.loli.net<span class="hljs-regexp">/2021/</span><span class="hljs-number">02</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/05/</span>OiyAj73IlBeozK6.jpg)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="插入视频"><a href="#插入视频" class="headerlink" title="插入视频"></a>插入视频</h2><ul><li>视频网站外链：<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=26418723&bvid=BV1Ss411p72p&cid=45397246&page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;"> </iframe></div><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs django"><span class="hljs-template-tag">&#123;% <span class="hljs-name">raw</span> %&#125;</span><br><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-bottom: 75%;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">iframe</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=26418723&amp;bvid=BV1Ss411p72p&amp;cid=45397246&amp;page=1&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">scrolling</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">border</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">framespacing</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">style</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0; top: 0;&quot;</span>&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-template-tag">&#123;% <span class="hljs-name">endraw</span> %&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="站内引用"><a href="#站内引用" class="headerlink" title="站内引用"></a>站内引用</h2></li></ul><p><code>&#123;% post_link slug [title] %&#125;</code></p><h2 id="常见报错"><a href="#常见报错" class="headerlink" title="常见报错"></a>常见报错</h2><ol><li><p>ValidationError: ‘null’ is not a string!</p><blockquote><p>文章无内容，属性未填写</p></blockquote></li><li><p>err: YAMLException: can not read a block mapping entry</p><blockquote><p>配置中出现了英文双引号，总之是违反了yaml语法</p></blockquote></li><li><p>迁移hexo到另一台设备可以参看</p><blockquote><p><a href="https://wungjyan.github.io/2018/08/17/move-hexo/">hexo博客迁移到另一台电脑 | wj’blog</a></p></blockquote></li></ol><h2 id="reference"><a href="#reference" class="headerlink" title="reference"></a>reference</h2><ol><li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">文档 | Hexo</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/">Hexo Fluid 用户手册</a></li><li><a href="http://www.54yongf.com/hexo/10.html">No10-原-hexo博文写作之博客生成generate常见错误集锦 | 移动开发技术小黑屋</a></li><li><a href="https://chrischen0405.github.io/2018/11/21/post20181121-2/">使用hexo发布文章报错can not read a block mapping entry | Chris的博客</a></li><li><a href="https://wungjyan.github.io/2018/08/17/move-hexo/">hexo博客迁移到另一台电脑 | wj’blog</a></li></ol><p><strong>以上です。</strong></p>]]></content>
    
    
